        h2 Thanks to
        .row.mt
          ul.list-unstyled
            li <a href="//github.com/BGuimberteau" title="Benjamin">Benjamin Guimberteau</a> for hosting the service
            li <a href="//blacktie.co" title="BlackTie">BlackTie.co</a> for the free theme
            li <a href="//iconsdb.com/" title="BlackTie">IconsDB</a> for their amazing icons
            li And <strong>eveyone</strong> who send me feedbacks !
      .col-md-6.col-md-offset-2.col-sm-12.text-center
        h2 About the author
        .mt
          img.img-circle(src='http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/458641ed4b2725b16edbf0192ca0b2f2', width='100', alt='Me!')
          h4 Dimitri Jorge
          p.
            I'm a developper currently living in Paris.
